  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The ACL 360 BAR™ is a versatile moving bar effect luminaire featuring (7) individual 15W RGBW 4-in-1 LEDs and the new advanced collimator optic lens, which combined produce a laser-like homogenized 4° color-changing beam from each lens which combined produce a 31° beam angle. Features include fast and precise16-bit continuous full 360° pan and tilt rotation, full individual pixel control, strobe, and selectable dimming curve effects, DMX, RDM (Remote Device Management), KlingNET™ and Art-NET support, 3/5pin XLR, Locking Power Cable, and RJ45 ethernet in/out connections, (6) button control full color 180° reversible menu display, 135W max power consumption, and a multi-voltage universal auto switching power supply (100-240v).",
